# toppy/hookdeck-deploy-cli 0.3.2 on npm - Libraries.io
created: 2026-03-02, last updated: 2026-06-10, [Read more](https://libraries.io/npm/@toppy%2Fhookdeck-deploy-cli)

Connections reference sources and destinations by name.
Both `filter` and `transformations` are shorthands that get converted to rules during deployment.
...
{
